321
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:46,440
This film 'The Duel of Two Beauties'.

322
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:48,960
Why is he here? Did he come to see me?

323
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,840
Her character

324
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,360
is very impressive in the film

325
00:25:51,360 --> 00:25:52,440
and fully developed.

326
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:53,080
Zheng Ying,

327
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:55,240
do you have anything you'd like to share with everyone?

328
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:57,160
Miss Zheng Ying, may I ask what role

329
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,360
you play in this film?

330
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:01,840
I play an assassin in this film.

331
00:26:02,040 --> 00:26:05,360
The cold-blooded, ruthless kind who's focused only on killing.

332
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:07,200
How do you understand this character?

333
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:10,000
Is she very different from who you are in real life?

334
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:12,280
I play an assassin in the film,

335
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,120
but that doesn't mean I have

336
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,400
the same personality in real life.

337
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,080
I still remember Miss Zheng Ying's

338
00:26:17,080 --> 00:26:19,000
story about being brave in love and hate.

339
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:22,000
Miss Zheng, do you currently have a new relationship?

340
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:26,960
I'm sorry.

341
00:26:27,360 --> 00:26:28,440
Please try to ask questions

342
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,640
related to the work.

343
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,480
Thank you.

344
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,320
I have someone I like.

345
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:37,880
Miss Zheng is indeed someone who loves and hates boldly.

346
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:38,840
What about him?

347
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,240
Does he know how you feel?

348
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:45,120
He should be very clear about it.

349
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:47,520
I'm just not sure

350
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:49,600
what kind of feelings he has for me.

351
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:51,440
I'm also looking forward to

352
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:53,560
him giving me a clear answer.

353
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:58,160
Mr. Shen,

354
00:26:58,520 --> 00:26:59,920
how do you feel right now?

355
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:03,440
What I mean is,

356
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,760
when capital generally doesn't favor

357
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:05,840
the film and TV industry,

358
00:27:05,840 --> 00:27:07,520
you suddenly returned to China to enter the industry.

359
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:08,640
During this time,

360
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:11,040
what are your thoughts about the industry?

361
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:15,850
To be honest,

362
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,720
I don't have any particular feelings.

363
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,780
I am a businessman.

364
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:21,340
Finding good projects

365
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,960
and good actors to work with

366
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,280
is my job.

367
00:27:25,360 --> 00:27:26,920
Anything beyond that,

368
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,530
I couldn't care less about.

369
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:32,240
Mr. Shen is indeed very rational.

370
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,120
In that case,

371
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:34,360
Mr. Shen seems more like

372
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,760
a cold-blooded killer.

373
00:27:36,280 --> 00:27:37,120
Indeed.

374
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,320
I'm sorry,

375
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:14,120
excuse me.

376
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:19,040
When luck turns against you,

377
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:20,920
everything goes wrong.

378
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,970
I have no feelings about this whatsoever.

379
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,760
I don't care at all.

380
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:45,760
Mr. Shen.

